{
  "_comment": [
    "─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────",
    " Bandhan AI — Firestore Composite Indexes",
    " Region: asia-south1 (Mumbai)",
    "─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────",
    "",
    " USAGE:",
    "   firebase deploy --only firestore:indexes",
    "",
    " NOTES:",
    " - Single-field indexes are created automatically by Firestore.",
    " - Only COMPOSITE indexes (queries on 2+ fields) need entries here.",
    " - If a query fails with 'FAILED_PRECONDITION', the error link",
    "   will auto-generate the index definition for you.",
    " - Indexes can take 5-10 minutes to build after deploy.",
    " - Collection names match lib/firebase/schema.ts → COLLECTIONS.",
    "─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────"
  ],

  "indexes": [
    {
      "_comment": "users: Discovery feed — filter by gender + sort by profileCompletion",
      "collectionGroup": "users",
      "queryScope": "COLLECTION",
      "fields": [
        { "fieldPath": "gender", "order": "ASCENDING" },
        { "fieldPath": "profileCompletion", "order": "DESCENDING" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_comment": "users: Discovery feed — filter by city + sort by profileCompletion",
      "collectionGroup": "users",
      "queryScope": "COLLECTION",
      "fields": [
        { "fieldPath": "city", "order": "ASCENDING" },
        { "fieldPath": "profileCompletion", "order": "DESCENDING" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_comment": "users: Discovery feed — filter by intent + sort by createdAt",
      "collectionGroup": "users",
      "queryScope": "COLLECTION",
      "fields": [
        { "fieldPath": "intent", "order": "ASCENDING" },
        { "fieldPath": "createdAt", "order": "DESCENDING" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_comment": "users: Discovery feed — filter by verificationLevel + sort by profileCompletion",
